name: FixedOrderComparator_addTest
description: Unit tests for the add functionality of the FixedOrderComparator class.

test_cases.name: testAddNewObject
test_cases.description: Tests adding a new object to the FixedOrderComparator and ensures it cannot be added again.

test_cases.name: testAddAfterLock
test_cases.description: Tests adding an object to the FixedOrderComparator after it has been locked by invoking compare.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqual
test_cases.description: Tests adding an object as equal to another object in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareAfterAdd
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison functionality of the FixedOrderComparator after adding objects.

test_cases.name: testEqualsAfterAdd
test_cases.description: Tests the equality of two FixedOrderComparator instances after adding the same objects.
